    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings located near coal mines, equipped with showers and clothes-drying facilities, typically found in England, Scotland, and Wales, and built for use by coal miners.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
